lead_paragraph: A.J. Green juggled oranges on a postgame show after a win earlier this season, showing off for the cameras. His latest sleight-of-hand got a touchdown and turned a game.

headline.print_headline: Green's Catch Highlights Bengals' 31-17 Win Over Browns
